  calories: 670 kcal
  fat: 34 g
  saturated fat: 15 g
  carbohydrates: 70 g
  sugar: 5 g
  protein: 17 g
  fiber: 6 g
  sodium: 2.8 g
  serving size: 630
source: https://www.hellofresh.be/recipes/risotto-met-groene-asperges-en-eekhoorntjesbrood-5a323c67c28800568f36bb72
